{"tid":2337570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家仲有冇儲舊紙幣","createTime":"2020-12-23T11:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T21:38:42.000Z","uid":225595,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83f053f3f8219cefea22f2833419b3468c3cda58","tid":2337570,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fdfg4aS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffdfg4aS.jpg&h=a0c2c95c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然好感觸 <br />\n<br />\n突然搵返啲舊紙幣 最遲 係2002年出產 當年仲有世界 個年巴西攞冠軍<br />\n<br />\n嘩 突然啲回憶返哂黎 唉 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說2002年當年小弟只係10歲 同一家人住埋一齊 好開心 家組仲未結婚 個時大家樂也融融 住政府樓 同鄰居關係好好，當時我地屋企打開門 我好鐘意出街玩 <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n當時回歸初期 大家都好融洽 。細個以為大家一家人會無風無浪 雖然現在都不太大變化<br />\n<br />\n個陣小四又落街識左班朋友踢波 係我自己主動既 咁玩左幾個月啦 我都以為會保持到關係。<br />\n<br />\n直到小五搬屋 情況有變化 冇哂朋友 搭 火車出去返學加埋補習 好累。我捱過左 小五小六既黑暗時期 升左上初中 以為初中冇咩變化 又唔係呀 同班朋友 幾岩玩 <br />\n<br />\n到中五會考完又一批人走 離離合合 我會考12分 留低原校 轉DSE 又識左班朋友 <br />\n<br />\n之後又讀左高級文憑 傻傻下 又黎到而家 雖然中途得左抑鬱症 但係而家己經克服左 唔洗食藥<br />\n<br />\n其實個個年代都有佢值得懷念之處 人大左冇諗咁多 大家努力工作 組織家庭 人既目標唔會得一個 會轉黎轉去 離離合合不需傷感 當然事實係好撚難<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小第都唔算細 90頭 希望可以開開心心再過活<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZX3eQR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZX3eQR8.jpg&h=ed655302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有女皇頭像 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2825dc74dbd4720209f8959df161caa5bf03b04b","tid":2337570,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSJvYcnDcXSZZ0a4KZWy5BUaIlmLYWEQRGUdA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSJvYcnDcXSZZ0a4KZWy5BUaIlmLYWEQRGUdA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=5e6dd51b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張野叫大綿胎，有你就正"},{"pid":"cefd4657247783a8853711ef0e57e27e7914b167","tid":2337570,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"打左成篇垃圾出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3572d339b38153b3352b489f430f9aaeb89c16","tid":2337570,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2825dc74dbd4720209f8959df161caa5bf03b04b","tid":2337570,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSJvYcnDcXSZZ0a4KZWy5BUaIlmLYWEQRGUdA&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSJvYcnDcXSZZ0a4KZWy5BUaIlmLYWEQRGUdA%26usqp%3DCAU&h=5e6dd51b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張野叫大綿胎，有你就正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33813ad7be01d5b5f59856a7d4a1455d80961b3","tid":2337570,"uid":225595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:36:36.000Z","msg":"冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbe786f1e9c45c3c91573bce7a84a716f4a9c93","tid":2337570,"uid":181819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"有張四十年代一仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d120058464898e5947137704425e4bbab9a0784","tid":2337570,"uid":246289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"加油 龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class